- cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with the retrieval of multimedia objects (i.e. interior design items) using both visual and textual modalities. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper may involve natural language processing techniques to process textual queries. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction): The paper may involve user studies or evaluations to assess the effectiveness of the proposed search engine.
